-- Sabesp to Provide Water, Sewage Services to Diadema for 30 Years
-- B y   F a b i o l a   M o u r a
-- 2013-08-29T21:57:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-29/sabesp-to-provide-water-sewage-services-to-diadema-for-30-years.html
 Cia. de Saneamento Basico do Estado
de Sao Paulo, Brazil’s largest water utility, signed an
agreement to take over the concession to provide water, sewage
services to Diadema, a neighboring city to Sao Paulo, according
to regulatory filing.  Sabesp will also take over the  labor force  from Saned, the
municipal company that currently provides the services. The
agreement is pending approval of Diadema’s local assembly,
according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabiola Moura in Sao Paulo at 
 fdemoura@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
